Single node:

Scientific Compution: a giant computer
        Act as a single computer, one component fail will halt the whole progress.
        Very expensive hardware. Very reliable. 

Commercial DC - Clos topology
        Cost efficiency matters, use cheap commodity hardwares.
        Something is always broken, no single point of failure.
        Built a reliable system from unrealibale components: TCP on top of unreliable network
        Error correcting code for corrupted data. 
        
        
